-(screaming)

54
00:02:36,906 --> 00:02:38,736
Please,
do not be alarmed.

55
00:02:38,825 --> 00:02:41,325
Our chefs are
just saying hello.

56
00:02:41,411 --> 00:02:42,661
Oh, okay.

57
00:02:42,745 --> 00:02:44,205
-(loudly) Hello!
-(screaming)

58
