I am Akira, your waiter.

62
00:02:53,798 --> 00:02:54,878
May I take your order?

63
00:02:54,966 --> 00:02:57,256
What would you recommend
for a family

64
00:02:57,343 --> 00:02:59,013
that's not sure
they should be here?

65
00:02:59,095 --> 00:03:01,595
The sushi surprise--
a little bit of everything.

66
00:03:01,681 --> 00:03:03,601
It is very non-threatening.

67
00:03:03,683 --> 00:03:04,933
I'll have
one of those.

68
00:03:05,018 --> 00:03:07,308
-Make it two.
-Akira, my good man.

69
00:03:07,395 --> 00:03:08,645
I'd like
two sharks, an octopus

70
00:03:08,730 --> 00:03:10,190
-and an eel.
-Very good.

71
00:03:10,273 --> 00:03:11,773
Do you have any giant squid?
The kind that drags men

72
00:03:11,858 --> 00:03:14,738
-to their deaths?
-Not today. Sir?

73
00:03:14,819 --> 00:03:17,239
It's so hard to choose.

74
00:03:17,322 --> 00:03:18,702
It all looks
so terrible.

75
00:03:18,781 --> 00:03:21,491
Just bring me one of these,
and one of these,

76
00:03:21,576 --> 00:03:22,536
and one of those.

77
00:03:22,619 --> 00:03:25,409
(grunting)

78
00:03:29,500 --> 00:03:30,670
(disapproving grunts)

79
00:03:30,752 --> 00:03:31,962
What do you think, master?

80
00:03:32,045 --> 00:03:34,375
No, no, no. Toshiro,
that squid looks like

81
00:03:34,464 --> 00:03:37,344
